          "name": "dragon_knight_elder_dragon_form",
          "name_loc": "Elder Dragon Form",
          "desc_loc": "Dragon Knight assumes the form of the Elder Dragon, increasing the range of his abilities, gaining bonus movement speed, and a ranged attack with various properties.  The Dragon evolves per level. The bonuses are cumulative. <br><br>Level 1 <font color=\"#9acd32\">Green</font>: Grants a corrosive damage over time that can also damage buildings.<br><br>Level 2 <font color=\"#FF0000\">Red</font>: Grants splash damage to the dragon's attacks.<br><br>Level 3 <font color=\"#87ceeb\">Blue</font>: Grants a debuff immunity piercing movement and attack frost slow on attack.",
          "lore_loc": "The dormant dragon power springs forth from within Davion, combining the powers of a legendary knight with a legendary Eldwurm.",
          "notes_loc": [
